<article>
<h2>Hello!</h2>
<p>This is my personal website where I publish some software I've written for
fun, or simply because I needed it.</p>
<p>Here you can find a few apps for Android smartphones, such as yet another
<a href="apps-android.html#binary-eye">barcode scanner app</a>,
or a minimalist
<a href="apps-android.html#pie-launcher">home screen launcher</a>
where you launch apps from a pie menu.</p>
<p>There are also some mini-games that you can play directly in your browser,
for example a little
<a href="games-casual.html#soyuz-404">space adventure</a>
or a quick
<a href="games-casual.html#bad-minton">ping-pong game</a>
for two players.</p>
<h3>Find me on:</h3>
